”Alexa, open my Barber”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my barber
des: My Barber is a simple skill. It helps you keep track of when you have your haircuts. Record when you have a haircut by letting Alexa know the date of the haircut. Alexa will also let you know how many days it's been since your last haircut when you start up the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
